txt.en: 'I maybe feel a little better? *cough cough* No, nevermind.'
'Kingsfoil didn't work either?! Oh no... This may be my end, friend.'
TBD Oh no that guy is dying!

The stolen medical supplies are hidden in Viznak's hideout.\n\nYou should find and collect the medical supplies.

'Rhadrog's condition is deteriorating rapidly. How could he have fallen ill so quickly from a simple mushroom? It is possible that goblin knew what he was talking about. Our supplies must be hidden nearby. See if you can find our medicines and heal our friend from Ithilien.'
Attempt to heal Rhadrog with Wanderbeard
Attempt to heal Rhadrog with Kingsfoil
You tell Faeron that your attempts to heal Rhadrog have all failed.\n\n'This is dire. If our medicines cannot help him, we may need to seek out the goblin.'
Attempt to heal Rhadrog with Maiden's Helm
Rhadrog has fallen ill from his exposure to the local flora of Agarnaith. Try to help him by finding the stolen medical supplies among the goblin's things.
